                  : "As a First Mover, we are building the world’s first innovative platform that seamlessly connects cryptocurrency exchanges with digital banking"
              }</strong
            >
            <ul>
              <li>
                {
                  locale === "ko"
                    ? "은행업과 디지털 자산 관리를 단일 플랫폼으로 결합"
                    : "Integrating banking and digital asset management within one unified platform"
                }
              </li>
              <li>
                {
                  locale === "ko"
                    ? "고객의 편의성과 편익성을 극대화하는 혁신적인 금융서비스"
                    : "Innovative financial services that maximize customer convenience and benefits"
                }
              </li>
              <li>
